Product description

Classic design with modern technology, this Fossil touchscreen smartwatch features a smoke stainless steel bracelet, and let's you track your heart rate, receive notifications, customize your dial and more. Smartwatches powered with Wear OS by Google are compatible with iPhone and Android phones. Stay in the know with messages and notifications delivered directly to your watch and stay in style with a customizable watch face that can be changed to match your look.

From the manufacturer

Read more



Notifications

Our smartwatches use Bluetooth technology to connect to your phone. When a notification or alert arrives, a gentle buzz lets you know right away.

Heart Rate Tracking

From running to yoga (and more), this smartwatch measures heart rate automatically during a workout.

Customizable Dials

Match your watch to your mood or personal style and swap your dial whenever you want. The choices are endless.

Read more



Untethered GPS

Leave your phone behind. Use untethered GPS to track your run's distance (and play your stored music) on your watch.

Custom and Social Dials

Make your own dial by personalizing select watch faces with your favorite Instagram or Facebook photos.Swap your dial whenever you want; the choices are endless.

Swimproof

Wash your hands, jump into the shower or hit the pool without fear. Your smartwatch will be safe and sound.
